Solanum umtuma 
<bibCitation author="Voronts. &amp; S.Knapp" box="[1053,1475,1294,1316]" journal="PhytoKeys" page="4" pageId="9" pageNumber="10" volume="8" year="2012">Voronts. &amp; S.Knapp, PhytoKeys 8: 4. 2012</bibCitation>
